HEADWORD: Country club
<hw>Coun"try club</hw>. <def>A club usually located in the suburbs or
vicinity of a city or town and devoted mainly to outdoor sports, and
usually having an attached golf course.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Country cousin</ent>⟦br⟧
